title: #92Noon: Montage/Bercich/Siny/Micheletti
description: Large part of the show dedicated to Vikings football and yesterday's loss in New England...Bercich in studio for a couple segments, Dave Sinykin on the Packers firing their coach, Pat Micheletti on the Wild, with calls and talkers throughout!
